{"tid":2162882,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"粒AMD 三星連球痴埋左","createTime":"2020-08-18T10:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T03:48:03.000Z","uid":250955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"862a3d00d9beef09e98498f091dc5d879114e68a","tid":2162882,"uid":250955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"係各位網友，早幾日開唔到機<br />\nMB debug 燈開機個陣CPU 個粒著左5秒就熄<br />\n無畫面<br />\n抆粒3600 出來發現有3點痴埋左<br />\n老母板msi b450 mortar<br />\n是咪要換U了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Qh81sb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Qh81sb.jpg&h=36333a3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86c854a5f2627445c6526cc63cac8fdb0221e4f1","tid":2162882,"uid":8011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"分返開佢地咪得囉"},{"pid":"34ad19d505ad727095f615af2bb1585128303542","tid":2162882,"uid":334722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"你唔識搞就唔好搞<br />\n我唔記得個三隻腳係唔係連埋通電既<br />\n個啲銀色既係焊點<br />\n假設佢本身係分開既<br />\n咁你要分開佢可以落焊寶再加風槍吹<br />\n如果佢本身唔係分開既你點吹個三點都係連埋<br />\n但應該唔會係分開<br />\n因為你部機正常冇咁熱令個焊點融化"},{"pid":"7e2835533eb389d1554c6199b516dbb377b001ee","tid":2162882,"uid":37660,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"係各位網友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcf7394366f3021620fb59727a1ecd227679f60","tid":2162882,"uid":201604,"like":0,"d